<view class="detail-con">
  <view class="detail-top">{{newsPage.title}}</view>
  <view class="detail-all">
    <view class="detail-img">
      <image src="{{imgUrl}}{{userInfo.headpath}}"></image>
    </view>
    <view class="detail-right">
      <text>{{newsPage.name}}</text>
      <text style="font-size:24rpx;">2019-05-03</text>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="detail-banner">
    <image src="{{imgUrl}}{{newsPage.filepath}}"></image>
  </view>
  <view class="detail-text">
    <rich-text nodes="{{newsPage.content}}"></rich-text>
    <view style="float:right" bindtap="good">点赞</view>
  </view>


    <view class="cu-list menu-avatar comment solids-top">
      <view class="cu-item">
        <view class="cu-avatar round" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/img/champion/Morgana.png);"></view>
        <view class="content">
          <view class="text-grey">莫甘娜</view>
          <view class="text-gray text-content text-df">
            凯尔，你被自己的光芒变的盲目。
          </view>
          <view class="bg-grey padding-sm radius margin-top-sm  text-sm">
            <view class="flex">
              <view>凯尔：</view>
              <view class="flex-sub">妹妹，你在帮他们给黑暗找借口吗?</view>
            </view>
          </view>
          <view class="margin-top-sm flex justify-between">
            <view class="text-gray text-df">2018年12月4日</view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="cu-item">
        <view class="cu-avatar round" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10006.jpg);"></view>
        <view class="content">
          <view class="text-grey">凯尔</view>
          <view class="text-gray text-content text-df">
            妹妹，如果不是为了飞翔，我们要这翅膀有什么用?
          </view>
          <view class="bg-grey padding-sm radius margin-top-sm  text-sm">
            <view class="flex">
              <view>莫甘娜：</view>
              <view class="flex-sub">如果不能立足于大地，要这双脚又有何用?</view>
            </view>
          </view>
          <view class="margin-top-sm flex justify-between">
            <view class="text-gray text-df">2018年12月4日</view>
            <view>
              <text class="cuIcon-appreciate text-gray"></text>
              <text class="cuIcon-messagefill text-gray margin-left-sm"></text>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
</view>
<view>
  <view class="send-msg">
    <input placeholder="请输入评论内容..." />
    <view>发送</view>
  </view>
</view>